window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Fae games will change you . . . but their love will ruin you.</p> <p>At least, that's what my mother told me. My mother had three rules:</p> <p>1. Never make a bargain with a fairy.</p> <p>2. Never enter the Waywoods on a hunting day.</p> <p>3. Never give the High Fae princes a reason to notice you.</p> <p>But even when I followed all the rules, the royal fae still took my family from me. So in one night I broke all three rules, and brought the kingdom to their knees.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
